"{\"uid\": \"velo.outsideonline.com-olympics-durango-roots-how-chris-blevins-and-riley-amos-punched-two-tickets-to-the-paris-olympics\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Powered byOutside It's no secret that Durango, Colorado is a bike town.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 72, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 48, \"end\": 56, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colorado\", \"score\": 0.9999999998753992, \"rank\": 1.1458903664994312e-10, \"text\": \"Colorado\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colorado\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colorado\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no secret\", \"from\": 23, \"to\": 32}, {\"ngram\": \"Durango\", \"from\": 38, \"to\": 45}, {\"ngram\": \"a bike town\", \"from\": 59, \"to\": 70}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From the hundreds of miles of trails that begin downtown and climb onto the surrounding mesas before heading into the high country above, to the legacy of champions - like first-ever cross-country world champ Ned Overend andVuelta a Espa\\u00f1a victor Sepp Kuss- who call Durango home, the small southwestern city is a really good place to ride bikes.\", \"from\": 76, \"to\": 422, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 323, \"end\": 332, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sepp_Kuss\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sepp Kuss\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sepp_Kuss\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sepp_Kuss\"}, {\"begin\": 343, \"end\": 350, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durango\", \"score\": 0.999999923015824, \"rank\": 7.698374089066126e-08, \"text\": \"Durango\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durango\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durango\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the hundreds\", \"from\": 81, \"to\": 93}, {\"ngram\": \"miles\", \"from\": 97, \"to\": 102}, {\"ngram\": \"trails\", \"from\": 106, \"to\": 112}, {\"ngram\": \"downtown\", \"from\": 124, \"to\": 132}, {\"ngram\": \"the surrounding mesas\", \"from\": 148, \"to\": 169}, {\"ngram\": \"the high country\", \"from\": 190, \"to\": 206}, {\"ngram\": \"the legacy\", \"from\": 217, \"to\": 227}, {\"ngram\": \"champions\", \"from\": 231, \"to\": 240}, {\"ngram\": \"the small southwestern city\", \"from\": 357, \"to\": 384}, {\"ngram\": \"a really good place\", \"from\": 388, \"to\": 407}, {\"ngram\": \"bikes\", \"from\": 416, \"to\": 421}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's such a good place, in fact, that since mountain biking became an Olympic sport, Durango has sent someone to the Games every time.\", \"from\": 424, \"to\": 558, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 509, \"end\": 516, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durango\", \"score\": 0.999999923015824, \"rank\": 7.698374089066126e-08, \"text\": \"Durango\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durango\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durango\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"such a good place\", \"from\": 429, \"to\": 446}, {\"ngram\": \"fact\", \"from\": 451, \"to\": 455}, {\"ngram\": \"mountain biking\", \"from\": 468, \"to\": 483}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic sport\", \"from\": 491, \"to\": 507}, {\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 526, \"to\": 533}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 537, \"to\": 546}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From Juli Furtado back in 1996 to Travis Brown and Ruthie Matthes in 2000 to Todd Wells from 2004 - 2012 and Howard Grotts in 2016, at least one of the riders repping Team USA has been flying the Durango flag as well.\", \"from\": 559, \"to\": 776, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 564, \"end\": 576, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Juli_Furtado\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Juli Furtado\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Juli_Furtado\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Juli_Furtado\"}, {\"begin\": 593, \"end\": 605, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Travis_Brown_(quarterback)\", \"score\": 0.655736832747639, \"rank\": 0.4000000000000053, \"text\": \"Travis Brown\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q14128148\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Travis_Brown_(quarterback)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Travis_Brown_(quarterback)\"}, {\"begin\": 610, \"end\": 624, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ruthie_Matthes\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ruthie Matthes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ruthie_Matthes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ruthie_Matthes\"}, {\"begin\": 636, \"end\": 646, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Todd_Wells\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Todd Wells\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Todd_Wells\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Todd_Wells\"}, {\"begin\": 726, \"end\": 734, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.991574563097755, \"rank\": 0.008444163244383822, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 755, \"end\": 762, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durango\", \"score\": 0.999999923015824, \"rank\": 7.698374089066126e-08, \"text\": \"Durango\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durango\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durango\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Howard\", \"from\": 668, \"to\": 674}, {\"ngram\": \"the riders\", \"from\": 707, \"to\": 717}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This year, in a fairly unprecedented scenario, the U.S. earned the maximum quota for mountain biking in Paris, and is sending four athletes to the Games.\", \"from\": 778, \"to\": 931, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 882, \"end\": 887, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.537972880583179e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a fairly unprecedented scenario\", \"from\": 792, \"to\": 823}, {\"ngram\": \"the U.S.\", \"from\": 825, \"to\": 833}, {\"ngram\": \"the maximum quota\", \"from\": 841, \"to\": 858}, {\"ngram\": \"mountain biking\", \"from\": 863, \"to\": 878}, {\"ngram\": \"four athletes\", \"from\": 904, \"to\": 917}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 921, \"to\": 930}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Any guesses where they are from?\", \"from\": 932, \"to\": 964, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Any guesses\", \"from\": 932, \"to\": 943}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Three of the four -Christopher Blevins, Riley Amos, andSavilia Blunk- claim ties to the city on the Animas, with Blevins and Amos born and raised in Durango and Blunk an alumna of Fort Lewis College.\", \"from\": 966, \"to\": 1165, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1006, \"end\": 1011, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Riley_Finn\", \"score\": 0.9999443509564624, \"rank\": 5.5287281962746345e-05, \"text\": \"Riley\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Riley_Finn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Riley_Finn\"}, {\"begin\": 1079, \"end\": 1086, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jerry_Blevins\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1542405121771202e-14, \"text\": \"Blevins\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jerry_Blevins\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jerry_Blevins\"}, {\"begin\": 1115, \"end\": 1122, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durango\", \"score\": 0.999999923015824, \"rank\": 7.698374089066126e-08, \"text\": \"Durango\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durango\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durango\"}, {\"begin\": 1146, \"end\": 1164, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fort_Lewis_College\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1451691802572343e-24, \"text\": \"Fort Lewis College\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fort_Lewis_College\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fort_Lewis_College\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the four -Christopher Blevins\", \"from\": 975, \"to\": 1004}, {\"ngram\": \"andSavilia\", \"from\": 1018, \"to\": 1028}, {\"ngram\": \"Blunk-\", \"from\": 1029, \"to\": 1035}, {\"ngram\": \"ties\", \"from\": 1042, \"to\": 1046}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 1050, \"to\": 1058}, {\"ngram\": \"the Animas\", \"from\": 1062, \"to\": 1072}, {\"ngram\": \"Amos\", \"from\": 1091, \"to\": 1095}, {\"ngram\": \"Blunk\", \"from\": 1127, \"to\": 1132}, {\"ngram\": \"an alumna\", \"from\": 1133, \"to\": 1142}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For Blevins, who also rode for the U.S. in Tokyo in 2021, competing in the Olympics is as much about representing Durango as it is the United States.\", \"from\": 1167, \"to\": 1316, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1210, \"end\": 1215, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9988081080789234, \"rank\": 0.001190704267705523, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 1302, \"end\": 1315, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999967155926519, \"rank\": 3.274512767795263e-06, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Blevins\", \"from\": 1171, \"to\": 1178}, {\"ngram\": \"the U.S.\", \"from\": 1198, \"to\": 1206}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1238, \"to\": 1250}, {\"ngram\": \"Durango\", \"from\": 1281, \"to\": 1288}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have felt like that my whole life on a mountain bike, really,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1318, \"to\": 1392, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my whole life\", \"from\": 1341, \"to\": 1354}, {\"ngram\": \"a mountain bike\", \"from\": 1358, \"to\": 1373}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Durango is something I am so eager to talk about and so proud of.\", \"from\": 1393, \"to\": 1459, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Durango\", \"from\": 1394, \"to\": 1401}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1405, \"to\": 1414}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It just feels natural.\", \"from\": 1460, \"to\": 1482, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It feels like it's synonymous with mountain biking in the U.S. at this point and I am really proud of that.\\\"\", \"from\": 1483, \"to\": 1591, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"mountain biking\", \"from\": 1518, \"to\": 1533}, {\"ngram\": \"the U.S.\", \"from\": 1537, \"to\": 1545}, {\"ngram\": \"this point\", \"from\": 1549, \"to\": 1559}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As synonymous as Durango is with mountain biking in the U.S., mountain biking in Durango is synonymous with Durango Devo.\", \"from\": 1593, \"to\": 1714, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1610, \"end\": 1617, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durango\", \"score\": 0.999999923015824, \"rank\": 7.698374089066126e-08, \"text\": \"Durango\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durango\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durango\"}, {\"begin\": 1674, \"end\": 1681, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durango\", \"score\": 0.999999923015824, \"rank\": 7.698374089066126e-08, \"text\": \"Durango\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durango\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durango\"}, {\"begin\": 1701, \"end\": 1708, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durango\", \"score\": 0.999999923015824, \"rank\": 7.698374089066126e-08, \"text\": \"Durango\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durango\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durango\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"mountain biking\", \"from\": 1626, \"to\": 1641}, {\"ngram\": \"the U.S.\", \"from\": 1645, \"to\": 1653}, {\"ngram\": \"mountain biking\", \"from\": 1655, \"to\": 1670}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The youth program, which is going on 20 years old, is where Blevins - and Amos and Grotts - cultivated their love of mountain biking.\", \"from\": 1715, \"to\": 1848, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The youth program\", \"from\": 1715, \"to\": 1732}, {\"ngram\": \"Blevins\", \"from\": 1775, \"to\": 1782}, {\"ngram\": \"Amos\", \"from\": 1789, \"to\": 1793}, {\"ngram\": \"their love\", \"from\": 1818, \"to\": 1828}, {\"ngram\": \"mountain biking\", \"from\": 1832, \"to\": 1847}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The program also served as the springboard for them to take the path more oriented toward racing.\", \"from\": 1849, \"to\": 1946, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The program\", \"from\": 1849, \"to\": 1860}, {\"ngram\": \"the springboard\", \"from\": 1876, \"to\": 1891}, {\"ngram\": \"the path\", \"from\": 1909, \"to\": 1917}, {\"ngram\": \"racing\", \"from\": 1939, \"to\": 1945}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's impossible to talk about Durango Devo without talking about Chad Cheeney.\", \"from\": 1948, \"to\": 2026, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1978, \"end\": 1985, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durango\", \"score\": 0.999999923015824, \"rank\": 7.698374089066126e-08, \"text\": \"Durango\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durango\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durango\"}, {\"begin\": 2013, \"end\": 2017, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chad\", \"score\": 0.9994774460184125, \"rank\": 0.0005139186849891168, \"text\": \"Chad\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chad\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chad\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Fort Lewis grad co-founded Devo in 2006 and has stood firmly at the helm of the non-profit since.\", \"from\": 2027, \"to\": 2128, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2031, \"end\": 2041, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fort_Lewis_College\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7712968374107376e-22, \"text\": \"Fort Lewis\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fort_Lewis_College\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fort_Lewis_College\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Devo\", \"from\": 2058, \"to\": 2062}, {\"ngram\": \"the helm\", \"from\": 2095, \"to\": 2103}, {\"ngram\": \"profit\", \"from\": 2115, \"to\": 2121}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Cheeney is partially responsible for one of Devo's core tenets: an age-based - rather than ability-based - programming structure.\", \"from\": 2129, \"to\": 2258, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Cheeney\", \"from\": 2129, \"to\": 2136}, {\"ngram\": \"Devo's core tenets\", \"from\": 2173, \"to\": 2191}, {\"ngram\": \"an age-based - rather than ability-based - programming structure\", \"from\": 2193, \"to\": 2257}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We believe that mountain biking skills and fitness will come naturally as a result of being part of an inclusive community of people who are excited about riding bikes.\", \"from\": 2260, \"to\": 2429, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"mountain biking skills\", \"from\": 2277, \"to\": 2299}, {\"ngram\": \"fitness\", \"from\": 2304, \"to\": 2311}, {\"ngram\": \"a result\", \"from\": 2335, \"to\": 2343}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 2353, \"to\": 2357}, {\"ngram\": \"an inclusive community\", \"from\": 2361, \"to\": 2383}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 2387, \"to\": 2393}, {\"ngram\": \"bikes\", \"from\": 2423, \"to\": 2428}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Riding in an age-based program helps build key friendships that ultimately make a successful rider.\", \"from\": 2430, \"to\": 2529, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an age-based program\", \"from\": 2440, \"to\": 2460}, {\"ngram\": \"key friendships\", \"from\": 2473, \"to\": 2488}, {\"ngram\": \"a successful rider\", \"from\": 2510, \"to\": 2528}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Any questions about the tenability of such a method?\", \"from\": 2529, \"to\": 2582, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\\"Any questions\", \"from\": 2529, \"to\": 2543}, {\"ngram\": \"the tenability\", \"from\": 2550, \"to\": 2564}, {\"ngram\": \"such a method\", \"from\": 2568, \"to\": 2581}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Just ask Blevins and Amos, or Sepp Kuss, who turned pro on the road, then won the Vuelta, after nearly a decade of mountain biking with his schoolmates in Durango.\", \"from\": 2583, \"to\": 2746, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2592, \"end\": 2599, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jerry_Blevins\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1542405121771202e-14, \"text\": \"Blevins\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jerry_Blevins\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jerry_Blevins\"}, {\"begin\": 2613, \"end\": 2622, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sepp_Kuss\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sepp Kuss\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sepp_Kuss\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sepp_Kuss\"}, {\"begin\": 2738, \"end\": 2745, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durango\", \"score\": 0.999999923015824, \"rank\": 7.698374089066126e-08, \"text\": \"Durango\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durango\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durango\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Amos\", \"from\": 2604, \"to\": 2608}, {\"ngram\": \"the road\", \"from\": 2642, \"to\": 2650}, {\"ngram\": \"the Vuelta\", \"from\": 2661, \"to\": 2671}, {\"ngram\": \"nearly a decade\", \"from\": 2679, \"to\": 2694}, {\"ngram\": \"his schoolmates\", \"from\": 2719, \"to\": 2734}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nevertheless, of the 1,000 kids who pass through Devo's ranks every year, not all of them go on to become Olympians or World Cup winners.\", \"from\": 2748, \"to\": 2885, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 1,000 kids\", \"from\": 2765, \"to\": 2779}, {\"ngram\": \"Devo's ranks\", \"from\": 2797, \"to\": 2809}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympians or World Cup winners\", \"from\": 2854, \"to\": 2884}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In fact, most do not.\", \"from\": 2886, \"to\": 2907, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fact\", \"from\": 2889, \"to\": 2893}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the percentage of riders who do go on to become professional cyclists outpaces most kids' cycling development programs.\", \"from\": 2908, \"to\": 3031, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"But the percentage\", \"from\": 2908, \"to\": 2926}, {\"ngram\": \"riders\", \"from\": 2930, \"to\": 2936}, {\"ngram\": \"professional cyclists outpaces\", \"from\": 2960, \"to\": 2990}, {\"ngram\": \"most kids' cycling development programs\", \"from\": 2991, \"to\": 3030}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's as if any aspiring pro (whether they know they are aspiring or not) who lives in Durango gets a ticket to a special portal that does not exist anywhere else.\", \"from\": 3033, \"to\": 3195, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3119, \"end\": 3126, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durango\", \"score\": 0.999999923015824, \"rank\": 7.698374089066126e-08, \"text\": \"Durango\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durango\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durango\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any aspiring pro\", \"from\": 3044, \"to\": 3060}, {\"ngram\": \"a ticket\", \"from\": 3132, \"to\": 3140}, {\"ngram\": \"a special portal\", \"from\": 3144, \"to\": 3160}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Durango is really special because we are introduced to competition in a really natural, low-pressure organic way where we are really pushing really hard learning these skills without really knowing you are doing it,\\\" said Riley Amos, who has swept the UCI U23 World Cup series this year.\", \"from\": 3197, \"to\": 3485, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3420, \"end\": 3425, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Riley_Finn\", \"score\": 0.9999443509564624, \"rank\": 5.5287281962746345e-05, \"text\": \"Riley\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Riley_Finn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Riley_Finn\"}, {\"begin\": 3450, \"end\": 3453, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Union_Cycliste_Internationale\", \"score\": 0.9999658615613208, \"rank\": 3.4139589549475664e-05, \"text\": \"UCI\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Union_Cycliste_Internationale\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Union_Cycliste_Internationale\"}, {\"begin\": 3458, \"end\": 3467, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIS_Alpine_Ski_World_Cup\", \"score\": 0.9994738446544053, \"rank\": 0.0005235458622007118, \"text\": \"World Cup\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIS_Alpine_Ski_World_Cup\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIS_Alpine_Ski_World_Cup\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Durango\", \"from\": 3198, \"to\": 3205}, {\"ngram\": \"competition\", \"from\": 3253, \"to\": 3264}, {\"ngram\": \"a really natural, low-pressure organic way\", \"from\": 3268, \"to\": 3310}, {\"ngram\": \"these skills\", \"from\": 3360, \"to\": 3372}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Take the Fort Lewis College short track races, for example.\", \"from\": 3487, \"to\": 3546, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3496, \"end\": 3514, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fort_Lewis_College\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1451691802572343e-24, \"text\": \"Fort Lewis College\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fort_Lewis_College\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fort_Lewis_College\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"example\", \"from\": 3538, \"to\": 3545}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Every Wednesday Chad and the Fort Lewis team would mark out a super janky short track through the bushes with a sack of flour,\\\" Amos said.\", \"from\": 3548, \"to\": 3687, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Every Wednesday Chad\", \"from\": 3549, \"to\": 3569}, {\"ngram\": \"the Fort Lewis team\", \"from\": 3574, \"to\": 3593}, {\"ngram\": \"a super janky short track\", \"from\": 3609, \"to\": 3634}, {\"ngram\": \"the bushes\", \"from\": 3643, \"to\": 3653}, {\"ngram\": \"a sack\", \"from\": 3659, \"to\": 3665}, {\"ngram\": \"flour\", \"from\": 3669, \"to\": 3674}, {\"ngram\": \"Amos\", \"from\": 3677, \"to\": 3681}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"At 16 I am lining up with the Fort Lewis team to do a short track.\", \"from\": 3688, \"to\": 3755, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Fort Lewis team\", \"from\": 3715, \"to\": 3734}, {\"ngram\": \"a short track\", \"from\": 3741, \"to\": 3754}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These guys are really strong, so racing with them every week I am learning tactics and getting a really good workout.\", \"from\": 3756, \"to\": 3873, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"These guys\", \"from\": 3756, \"to\": 3766}, {\"ngram\": \"tactics\", \"from\": 3831, \"to\": 3838}, {\"ngram\": \"a really good workout\", \"from\": 3851, \"to\": 3872}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But it's done with such low expectations, everyone is just cracking up going through the bushes.\\\"\", \"from\": 3874, \"to\": 3971, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"such low expectations\", \"from\": 3893, \"to\": 3914}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 3916, \"to\": 3924}, {\"ngram\": \"the bushes\", \"from\": 3959, \"to\": 3969}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Same goes for Durango's iconic group road ride, Tuesday Night Worlds.\", \"from\": 3973, \"to\": 4042, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3987, \"end\": 3994, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durango\", \"score\": 0.999999923015824, \"rank\": 7.698374089066126e-08, \"text\": \"Durango\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durango\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durango\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tuesday Night Worlds\", \"from\": 4021, \"to\": 4041}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My first one, I was like 17 on a borrowed Ross bike from Devo.\", \"from\": 4044, \"to\": 4107, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4087, \"end\": 4091, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ross_Geller\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.970068448061871e-22, \"text\": \"Ross\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ross_Geller\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ross_Geller\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Devo\", \"from\": 4102, \"to\": 4106}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am showing up with Todd [Wells], Ned [Overend], Payson [McElveen], Howard [Grotts], all these current pros that are extremely good.\", \"from\": 4108, \"to\": 4241, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Todd\", \"from\": 4129, \"to\": 4133}, {\"ngram\": \"[Overend\", \"from\": 4147, \"to\": 4155}, {\"ngram\": \"[McElveen\", \"from\": 4165, \"to\": 4174}, {\"ngram\": \"Howard\", \"from\": 4177, \"to\": 4183}, {\"ngram\": \"[Grotts\", \"from\": 4184, \"to\": 4191}, {\"ngram\": \"all these current pros\", \"from\": 4194, \"to\": 4216}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are going full gas into the wind 20 miles from town, having no idea how to draft or pull through.\", \"from\": 4242, \"to\": 4342, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"full gas\", \"from\": 4255, \"to\": 4263}, {\"ngram\": \"the wind\", \"from\": 4269, \"to\": 4277}, {\"ngram\": \"town\", \"from\": 4292, \"to\": 4296}, {\"ngram\": \"no idea\", \"from\": 4305, \"to\": 4312}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am motivated sheerly by the fact that if you get dropped it's a long way back to town.\\\"\", \"from\": 4343, \"to\": 4432, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the fact\", \"from\": 4369, \"to\": 4377}, {\"ngram\": \"a long way\", \"from\": 4407, \"to\": 4417}, {\"ngram\": \"town\", \"from\": 4426, \"to\": 4430}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As kids, athletes like Amos, Grotts, Blevins, and McElveen both knew and did not know the level they were being exposed to.\", \"from\": 4434, \"to\": 4557, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"kids\", \"from\": 4437, \"to\": 4441}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 4443, \"to\": 4451}, {\"ngram\": \"Amos\", \"from\": 4457, \"to\": 4461}, {\"ngram\": \"Grotts\", \"from\": 4463, \"to\": 4469}, {\"ngram\": \"Blevins\", \"from\": 4471, \"to\": 4478}, {\"ngram\": \"McElveen\", \"from\": 4484, \"to\": 4492}, {\"ngram\": \"the level\", \"from\": 4520, \"to\": 4529}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sure, most people know who the pros and Olympians in town are.\", \"from\": 4558, \"to\": 4620, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"most people\", \"from\": 4564, \"to\": 4575}, {\"ngram\": \"the pros\", \"from\": 4585, \"to\": 4593}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympians\", \"from\": 4598, \"to\": 4607}, {\"ngram\": \"town\", \"from\": 4611, \"to\": 4615}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But those men and women were also the same ones that were friends with their parents, or simply nice strangers they ran into on the trails.\", \"from\": 4621, \"to\": 4760, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"those men\", \"from\": 4625, \"to\": 4634}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 4639, \"to\": 4644}, {\"ngram\": \"the same ones\", \"from\": 4655, \"to\": 4668}, {\"ngram\": \"friends\", \"from\": 4679, \"to\": 4686}, {\"ngram\": \"their parents\", \"from\": 4692, \"to\": 4705}, {\"ngram\": \"simply nice strangers\", \"from\": 4710, \"to\": 4731}, {\"ngram\": \"the trails\", \"from\": 4749, \"to\": 4759}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You just have everything you need without realizing it,\\\" Amos said.\", \"from\": 4762, \"to\": 4829, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 4776, \"to\": 4786}, {\"ngram\": \"Amos\", \"from\": 4819, \"to\": 4823}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Just having so many resources, being surrounded by these pros, these group rides, these amazing trails.\", \"from\": 4830, \"to\": 4934, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"so many resources\", \"from\": 4843, \"to\": 4860}, {\"ngram\": \"these pros\", \"from\": 4882, \"to\": 4892}, {\"ngram\": \"these group\", \"from\": 4894, \"to\": 4905}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And, you are at altitude.\\\"\", \"from\": 4935, \"to\": 4961, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"altitude\", \"from\": 4951, \"to\": 4959}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Of all the mountain bike Olympians bred in Durango, none have come close to a podium at the Games, but that could change this year (note that Team USA's fourth rider, Haley Batten, who is not from Durango is also a serious medal contender).\", \"from\": 4963, \"to\": 5203, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5006, \"end\": 5013, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durango\", \"score\": 0.999999923015824, \"rank\": 7.698374089066126e-08, \"text\": \"Durango\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durango\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durango\"}, {\"begin\": 5105, \"end\": 5113, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.991574563097755, \"rank\": 0.008444163244383822, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 5130, \"end\": 5142, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haley_Batten\", \"score\": 0.9999978273623084, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Haley Batten\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haley_Batten\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haley_Batten\"}, {\"begin\": 5160, \"end\": 5167, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durango\", \"score\": 0.999999923015824, \"rank\": 7.698374089066126e-08, \"text\": \"Durango\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durango\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durango\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all the mountain bike\", \"from\": 4966, \"to\": 4987}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympians\", \"from\": 4988, \"to\": 4997}, {\"ngram\": \"none\", \"from\": 5015, \"to\": 5019}, {\"ngram\": \"a podium\", \"from\": 5039, \"to\": 5047}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 5051, \"to\": 5060}, {\"ngram\": \"a serious medal contender\", \"from\": 5176, \"to\": 5201}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On the men's side, that would be Blevins.\", \"from\": 5205, \"to\": 5246, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the men's side\", \"from\": 5208, \"to\": 5222}, {\"ngram\": \"Blevins\", \"from\": 5238, \"to\": 5245}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Although Amos has had a stand-out year in the U23 ranks, he's yet to race an elite World Cup.\", \"from\": 5247, \"to\": 5340, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5293, \"end\": 5296, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Under-23_sport\", \"score\": 0.9985421716153636, \"rank\": 0.0014546548943056555, \"text\": \"U23\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Under-23_sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Under-23_sport\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Amos\", \"from\": 5256, \"to\": 5260}, {\"ngram\": \"a stand-out year\", \"from\": 5269, \"to\": 5285}, {\"ngram\": \"an elite World Cup\", \"from\": 5321, \"to\": 5339}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And while Blevins has not had the most consistent year in terms of World Cup results, he believes he has enough experience, both at an Olympic Games and on the world stage, to show up when it counts.\", \"from\": 5341, \"to\": 5540, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5351, \"end\": 5358, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jerry_Blevins\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1542405121771202e-14, \"text\": \"Blevins\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jerry_Blevins\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jerry_Blevins\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the most consistent year\", \"from\": 5371, \"to\": 5395}, {\"ngram\": \"terms\", \"from\": 5399, \"to\": 5404}, {\"ngram\": \"World Cup results\", \"from\": 5408, \"to\": 5425}, {\"ngram\": \"enough experience\", \"from\": 5446, \"to\": 5463}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic Games\", \"from\": 5473, \"to\": 5489}, {\"ngram\": \"the world stage\", \"from\": 5497, \"to\": 5512}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I know what's possible now,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 5542, \"to\": 5580, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's that simple.\", \"from\": 5581, \"to\": 5599, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I know what's possible.\", \"from\": 5600, \"to\": 5623, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I know what I can do and what I can do on my best day, which is the same as any of those guys on their best day.\\\"\", \"from\": 5624, \"to\": 5737, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my best day\", \"from\": 5666, \"to\": 5677}, {\"ngram\": \"those guys\", \"from\": 5707, \"to\": 5717}, {\"ngram\": \"their best day\", \"from\": 5721, \"to\": 5735}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Regardless of what happens on the track in Paris, the story of how both Blevins and Amos got there might be the more important one.\", \"from\": 5739, \"to\": 5870, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5782, \"end\": 5787, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.537972880583179e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 5769, \"to\": 5778}, {\"ngram\": \"both Blevins\", \"from\": 5806, \"to\": 5818}, {\"ngram\": \"Amos\", \"from\": 5823, \"to\": 5827}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It began, as it often does for American athletes, with a points chase that began in earnest a year and a half ago.\", \"from\": 5871, \"to\": 5985, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5902, \"end\": 5910, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.999999993392521, \"rank\": 5.166878650618799e-09, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a points chase\", \"from\": 5926, \"to\": 5940}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At that point, the U.S. men's nations ranking hovered around 12th; if it stayed that way until May of 2024, that ranking would have earned them one Olympic berth in Paris.\", \"from\": 5986, \"to\": 6157, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6005, \"end\": 6009, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999932724677, \"rank\": 6.708148394757769e-09, \"text\": \"U.S.\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 6151, \"end\": 6156, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.537972880583179e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that point\", \"from\": 5989, \"to\": 5999}, {\"ngram\": \"12th\", \"from\": 6047, \"to\": 6051}, {\"ngram\": \"May\", \"from\": 6081, \"to\": 6084}, {\"ngram\": \"ranking\", \"from\": 6099, \"to\": 6106}, {\"ngram\": \"one Olympic berth\", \"from\": 6130, \"to\": 6147}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So, with the prodding of the federation, Blevins, Amos, and the US' other top points earner Bjorn Riley, got to work.\", \"from\": 6159, \"to\": 6276, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the prodding\", \"from\": 6168, \"to\": 6180}, {\"ngram\": \"the federation\", \"from\": 6184, \"to\": 6198}, {\"ngram\": \"Blevins\", \"from\": 6200, \"to\": 6207}, {\"ngram\": \"Amos\", \"from\": 6209, \"to\": 6213}]}, {\"sentence\": \"By the end of the year, they were inching closer to the eighth place - the threshold for sending two riders to the Olympics - but they were much too far to get their hopes up.\", \"from\": 6277, \"to\": 6452, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 6280, \"to\": 6287}, {\"ngram\": \"the year\", \"from\": 6291, \"to\": 6299}, {\"ngram\": \"the eighth place\", \"from\": 6329, \"to\": 6345}, {\"ngram\": \"the threshold\", \"from\": 6348, \"to\": 6361}, {\"ngram\": \"two riders\", \"from\": 6374, \"to\": 6384}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 6388, \"to\": 6400}, {\"ngram\": \"their hopes\", \"from\": 6437, \"to\": 6448}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then, they went to Arkansas.\", \"from\": 6454, \"to\": 6482, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6473, \"end\": 6481, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arkansas_Razorbacks\", \"score\": 0.5744743262243603, \"rank\": 0.7400050002395796, \"text\": \"Arkansas\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arkansas_Razorbacks\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arkansas_Razorbacks\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Going into the early-April US Pro Cup races in Fayetteville, the U.S. was ranked 10th.\", \"from\": 6484, \"to\": 6570, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6531, \"end\": 6543, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fayetteville_station\", \"score\": 0.9997503088976265, \"rank\": 0.00013394382571486806, \"text\": \"Fayetteville\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fayetteville_station\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fayetteville_station\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the early-April US Pro Cup races\", \"from\": 6495, \"to\": 6527}, {\"ngram\": \"the U.S.\", \"from\": 6545, \"to\": 6553}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After the weekend, they'd climbed the ladder two rungs into eighth.\", \"from\": 6571, \"to\": 6638, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the weekend\", \"from\": 6577, \"to\": 6588}, {\"ngram\": \"the ladder\", \"from\": 6605, \"to\": 6615}, {\"ngram\": \"eighth\", \"from\": 6631, \"to\": 6637}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The giant leap was in no small part due to the efforts of Amos, who was able to race both the U23 and elite XCO races in Arkansas, winning both of them.\", \"from\": 6639, \"to\": 6791, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6733, \"end\": 6736, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Under-23_sport\", \"score\": 0.9985421716153636, \"rank\": 0.0014546548943056555, \"text\": \"U23\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Under-23_sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Under-23_sport\"}, {\"begin\": 6760, \"end\": 6768, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arkansas_Razorbacks\", \"score\": 0.5744743262243603, \"rank\": 0.7400050002395796, \"text\": \"Arkansas\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arkansas_Razorbacks\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arkansas_Razorbacks\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The giant leap\", \"from\": 6639, \"to\": 6653}, {\"ngram\": \"no small part\", \"from\": 6661, \"to\": 6674}, {\"ngram\": \"the efforts\", \"from\": 6682, \"to\": 6693}, {\"ngram\": \"Amos\", \"from\": 6697, \"to\": 6701}, {\"ngram\": \"elite XCO races\", \"from\": 6741, \"to\": 6756}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Still, with nearly two more months left in the Olympics qualifying calendar, it wasn't guaranteed that the U.S would send two men (the women had already s