\"to\": 7362}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We kept everything tight and motivated for the collective good, but tensions were high this spring,\\\" Amos said.\", \"from\": 7365, \"to\": 7477, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 7374, \"to\": 7384}, {\"ngram\": \"the collective good\", \"from\": 7409, \"to\": 7428}, {\"ngram\": \"tensions\", \"from\": 7434, \"to\": 7442}, {\"ngram\": \"Amos\", \"from\": 7467, \"to\": 7471}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Chris was pushing, and I was really trying to figure out how and where to focus.\", \"from\": 7478, \"to\": 7559, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Chris\", \"from\": 7479, \"to\": 7484}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We were both having to try and float so many circles.\", \"from\": 7560, \"to\": 7613, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"so many circles\", \"from\": 7597, \"to\": 7612}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But when we win together we win together.\", \"from\": 7614, \"to\": 7655, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Brazil was such a huge moment.\\\"\", \"from\": 7656, \"to\": 7687, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7656, \"end\": 7662, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil\", \"score\": 0.9677972402996794, \"rank\": 0.03256190299166508, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"such a huge moment\", \"from\": 7667, \"to\": 7685}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Amos particularly struggled with the dilemma of what his \\\"employers [trade team] thought was best versus what the federation thought was best versus what I thought was best,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 7689, \"to\": 7872, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Amos\", \"from\": 7689, \"to\": 7693}, {\"ngram\": \"the dilemma\", \"from\": 7722, \"to\": 7733}, {\"ngram\": \"his \\\"employers\", \"from\": 7742, \"to\": 7756}, {\"ngram\": \"trade team\", 