 to do with it,\\\" Amos said.\", \"from\": 8158, \"to\": 8207, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"That 1000 percent\", \"from\": 8159, \"to\": 8176}, {\"ngram\": \"Amos\", \"from\": 8197, \"to\": 8201}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's rare that competitors have such a good relationship in general.\", \"from\": 8208, \"to\": 8277, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"competitors\", \"from\": 8224, \"to\": 8235}, {\"ngram\": \"such a good relationship\", \"from\": 8241, \"to\": 8265}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We have a lot of heritage, growing up together to an extent.\", \"from\": 8278, \"to\": 8338, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 8286, \"to\": 8291}, {\"ngram\": \"heritage\", \"from\": 8295, \"to\": 8303}, {\"ngram\": \"an extent\", \"from\": 8328, \"to\": 8337}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That relationship, our Durango roots, for sure it was a motivating force.\", \"from\": 8339, \"to\": 8412, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8362, \"end\": 8369, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durango\", \"score\": 0.999999923015824, \"rank\": 7.698374089066126e-08, \"text\": \"Durango\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durango\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durango\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"That relationship\", \"from\": 8339, \"to\": 8356}, {\"ngram\": \"a motivating force\", \"from\": 8393, \"to\": 8411}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Under different circumstances, I am sure people would have done things differently.\\\"\", \"from\": 8413, \"to\": 8497, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"different circumstances\", \"from\": 8419, \"to\": 8442}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 8454, \"to\": 8460}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 8477, \"to\": 8483}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For both of our own reasons, we wanted to get two spots,\\\" Blevins said.\", \"from\": 8499, \"to\": 8571, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our own reasons\", \"from\": 8512, \"to\": 8527}, {\"ngram\": \"two spots\", \"from\": 8546, \"to\": 8555}, {\"ngram\": \"Blevins\", \"from\": 8558, \"to\": 8565}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But if it was a matter of a little extra work to get each other there, both of us, and Bjorn, we were gonna do it.\", \"from\": 8572, \"to\": 8687, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a matter\", \"from\": 8587, \"to\": 8595}, {\"ngram\": \"a little extra work\", \"from\": 8599, \"to\": 8618}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 8652, \"to\": 8654}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Riley and I are a product of the same circle.\", \"from\": 8688, \"to\": 8733, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Riley\", \"from\": 8688, \"to\": 8693}, {\"ngram\": \"a product\", \"from\": 8704, \"to\": 8713}, {\"ngram\": \"the same circle\", \"from\": 8717, \"to\": 8732}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The backing we have of knowing how many Durango Olympians have gone before us, that's given me confidence my whole life to know what's possible.\\\"\", \"from\": 8734, \"to\": 8879, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8774, \"end\": 8781, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durango\", \"score\": 0.999999923015824, \"rank\": 7.698374089066126e-08, \"text\": \"Durango\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durango\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durango\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The backing\", \"from\": 8734, \"to\": 8745}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 8809, \"to\": 8811}, {\"ngram\": \"confidence\", \"from\": 8829, \"to\": 8839}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Watch Durango, er Amos and Blevins, take on the world during the men's Olympic mountain bike race on Monday, July 29 at 5:00 a.m. PST.\", \"from\": 8881, \"to\": 9015, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Watch Durango\", \"from\": 8881, \"to\": 8894}, {\"ngram\": \"Amos\", \"from\": 8899, \"to\": 8903}, {\"ngram\": \"Blevins\", \"from\": 8908, \"to\": 8915}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 8925, \"to\": 8934}, {\"ng